text: Joshua Lautenschlager Kaul (born February 2, 1981) is an American lawyer and Democratic politician. He has been the 45th Attorney General of Wisconsin since January 2019. His mother, Peg Lautenschlager, was also Wisconsin's attorney general. Kaul was born in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. He was raised in Wisconsin in Oshkosh and Fond du Lac. ==References== ==Other websites== * Wisconsin Attorney General's Office * * * Category:Wisconsin attorneys general Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Pittsburgh Category:Lawyers from Pittsburgh Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:People from Fond du Lac, Wisconsin Category:People from Oshkosh, Wisconsin
